00:20:04,553 --> 00:20:05,414
For example, in a

429
00:20:06,455 --> 00:20:11,960
in budget cuts, they don't tell you press the trigger to grab an object, they just tell you

430
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:17,725
try picking stuff up. And you do that naturally, because it feels natural. So that's super,

431
00:20:17,725 --> 00:20:23,131
super interesting. As well as even better, closing things and interacting with things

432
00:20:23,131 --> 00:20:28,856
just by touching them without pressing any button, like closing a drawer with your forehead.

