503
00:24:27,408 --> 00:24:30,049
What do you think, or how would you

504
00:24:30,049 --> 00:24:32,070
introduce item shops or currency shops

505
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:33,891
in free-to-play mobile games?

506
00:24:33,891 --> 00:24:36,892
Because they are often part of the tutorial,

507
00:24:36,892 --> 00:24:39,393
and I think there's no good way.

508
00:24:39,393 --> 00:24:42,694
Right, so I don't think it's.

509
00:24:43,803 --> 00:24:46,284
I don't think it's necessarily a thing with mobile games

510
00:24:46,284 --> 00:24:48,404
or free-to-play games, but you're

511
00:24:48,404 --> 00:24:51,405
talking about a UI element, like introducing a mechanic

512
00:24:51,405 --> 00:24:52,606
through the UI.

513
00:24:52,606 --> 00:24:54,126
And basically, the secret of that

514
00:24:54,126 --> 00:24:57,587
